de_leisure_v2 - 2005 by Kuma

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent the terrorists from bombing the weapon stashes

Terrorists: Destroy one of the weapon stashes by planting the bomb



Unpack into your counterstrike source folder.

Changes since version 1

Map has been rebuilt to reduce the lag. 
Skybox and surrounding buildings have changed 
Added a few custom textures 
Closed off the front door and made a hole through a wall for T's to enter giving cts a better chance of leaving spawn (but not to much) 
Removed some items to make more space 
Fixed SOLID_VPHYSICS errors.
